window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The war continues.</b></p> <p>Brad, Jake, and Sam continue to survive and thrive in the new world. But just as they start to establish themselves, a new threat arrives. One that even the collective fears. Throwing the balance into chaos once more. But with their growing powers and alliances, humanity isn't out of the game yet.</p> <p><i>Apocalypse Online</i> is a LitRPG/gamelit post-apocalypse fantasy series filled with action, adventure, aliens, and snarky AIs.</p> <p>If you are a fan of System Apocalypse, Defiance of the Fall, or the Sun Shadow series, you'll love <i>Apocalypse Online</i>!</p>"; 
